\newlabel{fig:phenotype}{{8}{21}{Phenotype consistency: oracle (blue) vs.\ predicted (red) parameters in PC1--PC2 space. Lines connect corresponding leaves. The predicted parameters occupy the same region as the oracle parameters, preserving phenotypic structure}{figure.8}{}}
